The '''Djo family''' was a group of [[Witches of Dathomir|Dathomiri witches]]. They were the leaders of the [[Singing Mountain Clan]] and became the royal family of the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]]. Members included:

*[[Augwynne Djo]], [[Singing Mountain Clan]] matriarch
*[[Barukka]], Augwynne's first daughter
*[[Gethzerion]], Augwynne's second daughter
*[[Allaya Djo]], Augwynne's third daughter
*[[Kara'Teel]], Augwynne's fourth daughter
*[[Aelta]], Augwynne's adopted daughter
*[[Chastina]], Augwynne's adopted daughter
*[[Teneniel Djo]], Allaya's daughter, [[Queen Mother]] of the Hapes Consortium
*[[Tenel Ka Djo|Tenel Ka Chume Ta' Djo]], Teneniel's daughter, Queen Mother of the Hapes Consortium
*[[Allana Djo Solo]], daughter of Tenel Ka and [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]], [[Chume'da]] of the Hapes Consortium

